            {
                "id": "925191110974930964",
                "type": 0,
                "content": "When I first started writing AnchorPy I thought I could be real clever and just make it a thin wrapper around the Rust client but then I realised that it couldn\u2019t possibly be as thin as I wanted. But I still want to remove as much Python logic as possible",
