            {
                "id": "925181471151513660",
                "type": 0,
                "content": "I don\u2019t *think* the performance benefits of Rust in AnchorPy would be that significant because the one place where I\u2019m aware I\u2019m doing some dumb slow stuff isn\u2019t in the hot path (it\u2019s in creating the Program object).\n\nBut maybe creating transactions and signing them is just slow in Python? I haven\u2019t compared the two yet",
